==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Retrocede
<hw>Re"tro*cede</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>retrocedere</ets>;
<ets>retro</ets> backward, back + <ets>cedere</ets> to go. See
<er>Cede</er>.]</ety> <def>To go back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

